item.title: About
item.description: Welcome! This is my personal website for recording daily life and sharing knowledge. About Me I am a mathematics student and avid dreamer, lived in China. I am interested in mathematics, computer science, software, Linux and Vim. I got my Bachelor’s in Mathematics and Bachelor’s in Finance from SDUFE. Some config of my computer: OS: macOS 12.0 Shell: Zsh 5.8 Terminal: Alacritty and iTerm2 Terminal Font: Fira Code Nerd Font
